OPNsense Automation Plugin

Provides centralized management of multiple OPNsense firewall instances
from a single OPNsense installation, including:

- Status dashboard with version overview for all managed instances
- One-click and scheduled OPNsense firmware updates across instances
- Zenarmor (os-sensei) version monitoring and update management
- Zenarmor engine watchdog with automatic restart capability
- Configuration backup with retention policy and unified diff view
- Secure API-credential management per managed host

